Somizi and Mohale's highly anticipated white wedding is finally taking place today. The couple affectionately known as Somhale hosted friends last night for a pyjama party. Singer Vusi Nova was one of the guests at the party. Meanwhile, Somizi has revealed via Instagram that they will change three times at the white wedding. The couple's traditional wedding took place at Kibler Park, south of Joburg. They have however not yet revealed the venue of their white wedding. Love A post shared by  Somizi (@somizi) on Jan 29, 2020 at 11:34am PST 3 changes tomorrow #somhalewhitewedding A post shared by  Somizi (@somizi) on Jan 29, 2020 at 12:36pm PST 